    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find for the discerning buyer. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no chips or scratches, while the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with the engine and transmission operating exactly as they did the day it left the factory. Every feature and electronic component works flawlessly, and the service history is comprehensive, reflecting the meticulous care this vehicle has received. You will not find a better-maintained example on the market.",
