    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle offers a harmonious blend of performance and reliability. Meticulously maintained and showcasing a clean aesthetic profile, it stands as a testament to quality ownership. Prospective buyers will appreciate the robust mechanical integrity and the refined interior appointments. This selection represents a sophisticated investment for the discerning driver seeking a dependable, high-caliber driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-maintained, super reliable, and still looks great on the road. It's been my daily driver and has never let me down! Perfect for anyone looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready for many more adventures. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power unit utilizes eight independent throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to deliver linear power through its 8,400 RPM redline. The 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise engagement, paired with the Variable M Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. This example features Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable suspension geometry and damping. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle body actuators, ensuring the VANOS system and valvetrain operate at peak performance. A mechanically robust example of the final naturally aspirated M-car, ready for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Regular service history. Runs well.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and presents beautifully in its original factory finish. The exterior retains a deep gloss, though upon close inspection, you\u2019ll find the typical minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin remains a serene environment; the leather seats are supple with only slight bolster wear on the driver\u2019s side, and every button, switch, and digital display operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has followed a strict maintenance schedule, with a recent service including a fresh oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It drives straight and true, offering a smooth, rattle-free experience that reflects its history of responsible ownership. This is an excellent opportunity to own a reliable, well-documented vehicle that balances performance with everyday practicality.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, characterized by its consistent maintenance history and robust mechanical integrity. Demonstrating impressive road manners and a well-preserved aesthetic, this model offers a sophisticated driving experience without compromise. Every system has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our exacting standards for safety and performance. This represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a balance of luxury, reliability, and long-term value.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a smooth, worry-free ride. It\u2019s been well-loved and well-kept, so it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner. If you're looking for a dependable set of wheels that still looks great on the road, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
