      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 1995 BMW M3, featuring the S50 3.0L inline-six with crisp VANOS engagement. This E36 retains its factory ZF 5-speed manual transmission and limited-slip differential, providing exceptional tactile feedback. Recent service includes a full cooling system overhaul and reinforced subframe mounts to address common chassis fatigue points. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains robust, pulling hard through the rev range with a neutral handling balance. Riding on staggered Style 22 'Sunflowers,' this M-car represents a high-performance baseline for the driver seeking mechanical purity over a trailer queen.",
